snippet.title: ClassiCube trailer
snippet.description:
PLAY CLASSICUBE AT: http://www.classicube.net/
FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/ClassiCube

ClassiCube is a free and easy-to-use substitute for Minecraft Classic, an early version of the popular game Minecraft, only better.

With ClassiCube's client, you'll be building amazing things, playing fun minigames, and roleplaying in no time at all! ClassiCube even added features that will improve your time playing. Servers can, for example, change the sky color, light color, enable new blocks, and more!

ClassiCube client works with all servers on our server list. This means you can play with your friends in tons of servers!
